          "result": "canonicalizeS r =\n    lpField r.method\n  # lpField r.body\n  # join [ lpHeader h | h <- r.hdrs ]\n  # lpField r.path\n  # (split r.timestamp : [8][8])"
        }
      ],
      "body": "canonicalizeS r =\n    lpField r.method\n  # lpField r.body\n  # join [ lpHeader h | h <- r.hdrs ]\n  # lpField r.path\n  # (split r.timestamp : [8][8])",
      "doc": [
        "Concrete canonicalize: length-prefixed method, body, headers (with",
